title: Urevassnutene
text: Urevassnutane or Urevassnutene is a <a href="mountain">mountain</a> in the municipality of <a href="Bykle">Bykle</a> in <a href="Agder">Agder</a> county, <a href="Norway">Norway</a>. The tall mountain has a <a href="topographic%20prominence">topographic prominence</a> of . The mountain sits in the <a href="Setesdalsheiene">Setesdalsheiene</a> mountains and it sits on the southern shore of the lake <a href="Store%20Urevatn">Store Urevatn</a>. The nearest road lies about to the east and the road comes from the village of <a href="Bykle%20%28village%29">Bykle</a>, about to the southwest.
